Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> PROGRAM ID statements END
Rule 2     statements -> statement
Rule 3     statements -> statements statement
Rule 4     statement -> declaration
Rule 5     var_dec -> ID
Rule 6     var_dec -> ID LPAREN NUMBER RPAREN
Rule 7     id_list -> var_dec
Rule 8     id_list -> id_list COMMA var_dec
Rule 9     type -> INTEGER
Rule 10    type -> REAL
Rule 11    type -> LOGICAL
Rule 12    declaration -> type id_list

